110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Mesh</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-slate-600\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z\\\"/><circle cx=\\\"12\\\" cy=\\\"12\\\" r=\\\"3\\\"/></svg>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Sys</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </nav>\\n\\n    <!-- Screen Reflection -->\\n    <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-tr from-white/5 to-transparent\\\"></div>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Sleek Interface\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Sleek Interface\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-full h-full bg-[#090A0D] flex items-center justify-center p-8 text-slate-200 font-sans\\\">\\n  <div class=\\\"w-[375px] h-[667px] bg-[#12141C] rounded-[48px] border-[8px] border-[#252833] shadow-[0_0_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)] relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n    \\n    <!-- Status Bar -->\\n    <div class=\\\"h-12 w-full flex justify-between items-center px-8 pt-4\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-[12px] font-bold tracking-tight\\\">12:45</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-1.5 items-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-4 h-3 border border-slate-500 rounded-[2px] relative\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute left-0 top-0 h-full bg-cyan-500 w-4/5\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-3 h-3\\\">\\n          <svg viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\" class=\\\"text-cyan-500\\\"><path d=\\\"M12 21l-12-18h24z\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Main Control Panel -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 px-6 pt-6 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n      <header class=\\\"mb-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-1\\\">\\n          <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white\\\">Local Node 01</h1>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-cyan-500 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\\\">Active</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-slate-500 text-xs font-mono\\\">IP: 192.168.1.154 \342\200\242 v2.4.1</p>\\n      </header>\\n\\n      <!-- Main Toggle -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#1C1F2B] rounded-3xl p-6 mb-6 border border-white/5 shadow-inner\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-6\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-slate-400 text-sm mb-1\\\">Master Switch</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-white font-medium\\\">Living Room LED</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-14 h-8 bg-cyan-600 rounded-full relative p-1\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"absolute right-1 w-6 h-6 bg-white rounded-full shadow-lg\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#252936] p-4 rounded-2xl\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase mb-1 tracking-widest\\\">Brightness</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xl font-light text-white\\\">84<span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 ml-0.5\\\">%</span></p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#252936] p-4 rounded-2xl\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase mb-1 tracking-widest\\\">Temp</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xl font-light text-white\\\">24.5<span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 ml-0.5\\\">\302\260C</span></p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Mesh Nodes -->\\n      <div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-4\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Mesh Network (3)</h2>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-700 border-t-cyan-500\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n          <!-- Peer Node 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between bg-[#171A24] p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#252936] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 font-mono text-sm\\\">02</div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-white\\\">Kitchen ESP</p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Signal: -64dBm</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_8px_#10b981]\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <!-- Peer Node 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between bg-[#171A24] p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 opacity-80\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#252936] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500 font-mono text-sm\\\">03</div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-300\\\">Bedroom S3</p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Signal: -78dBm</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/50\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <!-- Peer Node 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between bg-[#171A24] p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 opacity-60\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#252936] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 font-mono text-sm\\\">04</div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-400\\\">Garden Cam</p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-600\\\">Signal: -92dBm</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Bottom Navigation -->\\n    <nav class=\\\"h-20 w-full bg-[#1A1D27] border-t border-white/5 px-8 flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-cyan-500\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\\\"/></svg>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Control</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-slate-600\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.2