e implications of the \"DICA DE ARQUITETURA MULTI-N\303\223\" tip, specifically the automatic enabling of CORS headers for the ESPAsyncWebServer. I need to understand how this facilitates direct data exchange between nodes via AJAX calls, eliminating the need for an external cloud server. The goal is to evaluate if this is suitable for my needs, and verify that this is secure.\n\n\n"
