        target_content: "void loop() {\n  // mDNS loop e verifica\303\247\303\243o de rede local a  return (\n    <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-5\">\n      {/* Sub-Tab Navigation Bar */}\n      <div className=\"flex bg-[#12141C] p-1.5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 shadow-inner w-full max-w-sm md:max-w-md mx-auto mb-1\">\n        <button\n          type=\"button\"\n          onClick={() => setSubTab(\'CODE\')}\n          className={`flex-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-2 px-3 text-xs font-bold rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer ${\n            subTab === \'CODE\'\n              ? \'bg-cyan-500 text-slate-950 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(6,182,212,0.25)]\'\n              : \'text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-200 hover:bg-white/5\'\n          }`}\n        >\n          <FileCode className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n          <span>Esquemas & C\303\263digo</span>\n        </button>\n        <button\n          type=\"button\"\n          onClick={() => setSubTab(\'OTA\')}\n          className={`flex-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-2 px-3 text-xs font-bold rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer ${\n            subTab === \'OTA\'\n              ? \'bg-cyan-500 text-slate-950 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(6,182,212,0.25)]\'\n              : \'text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-200 hover:bg-white/5\'\n          }`}\n        >\n          <Cpu className=\"w-4 h-4 animate-pulse\" />\n          <span>Atualiza\303\247\303\243o OTA (Simulador)</span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n\n      {subTab === \'CODE\' ? (\n        <>\n          {/* Introduction Card */}\n          <div className=\"bg-[#1C1F2B] p-5 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 shadow-inner backdrop-blur-sm\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n              <BookOpen className=\"w-4 h-4 text-cyan-400\" />\n              <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-300\">Como instalar no ESP32</h4>\n            </div>\n            <p className=\"text-neutral-400 text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">\n              Como este app React \303\251 focado em <strong className=\"text-neutral-200\">baixo consumo de mem\303\263ria</strong>, ele pode ser gravado inteiramente no ESP32. Quando o seu ESP32 inicializa em modo Wi-Fi, ele cria a sua rede ou se conecta ao roteador, servindo esta mesma p\303\241gina aos celulares e computadores conectados na mesma rede local!\n            </p>\n\n            {/* Steps Guide */}\n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3.5 mt-5\">\n              <div className=\"bg-[#12141C] p-3.5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 shadow-inner\">\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 bg-[#252936] border border-white/5 rounded-lg text-cyan-400\">PASSO 1</span>\n                <h5 className=\"font-bold text-[11px] text-slate-200 mt-2\">Compilar a Interface</h5>\n                <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-slate-500 mt-1 leading-normal\">\n                  Execute <code className=\"bg-[#1C1F2B] text-slate-400 px-1 py-0.5 rounded\">npm run build</code> para gerar arquivos unificados de baixo footprint na pasta <code className=\"text-slate-400\">dist/</code>.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"bg-[#12141C] p-3.5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 shadow-inner\">\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 bg-[#252936] border border-white/5 rounded-lg text-cyan-400\">PASSO 2</span>\n                <h5 className=\"font-bold text-[11px] text-slate-200 mt-2\">Gzip & Prepara\303\247\303\243o</h5>\n                <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-slate-550 mt-1 leading-normal\">\n                  Comprima o HTML buildado para <code className=\"text-slate-450 font-mono border-none\">.gz</code>. Isso reduz seu peso para cerca de <strong className=\"text-cyan-400 font-bold\">22KB</strong>, ocupando pouqu\303\255ssimo espa\303\247o!\n                </p>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"bg-[#12141C] p-3.5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 shadow-inner\">\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 bg-[#252936] border border-white/5 rounded-lg text-cyan-400\">PASSO 3</span>\n                <h5 className=\"font-bold text-[11px] text-slate-200 mt-2\">Grava\303\247\303\243o Arduino</h5>\n                <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-slate-500 mt-1 leading-normal\">\n                  Copie o c\303\263digo C++ abaixo e fa\303\247a o upload no seu ESP32 usando a IDE cl\303\241ssica ou VSCode PlatformIO.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Code exporter container */}\n          <div className=\"bg-[#1C1F2B] p-5 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 flex flex-col shadow-inner\">\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-[#252833]/60 mb-4 flex-wrap gap-2\">\n              {/* Tabs for select flashing architecture */}\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                <FileCode className=\"w-4 h-4 text-cyan-400\" />\n                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-300 mr-2\">C\303\263digo Firmware Arduino</h4>\n                \n                <div className=\"flex bg-[#12141C] p-1 rounded-xl border border-white/5\">\n                  <button \n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={() => setExportMethod(\'PROGMEM\')}\n                    className={`text-[9.5px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-lg transition-all cursor-pointer ${exportMethod === \'PROGMEM\' ? \'bg-cyan-500 text-slate-950 font-mono font-bold\' : \'text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-355\'}`}\n                  >\n                    PROGMEM (Inline Flash)\n                  </button>\n                  <button \n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={() => setExportMethod(\'LITTLEFS\')}\n                    className={`text-[9.5px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-lg transition-all cursor-pointer ${exportMethod === \'LITTLEFS\' ? \'bg-cyan-500 text-slate-950 font-mono font-bold\' : \'text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-355\'}`}\n                  >\n                    LittleFS Partition\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <button \n                type=\"button\"\n                onClick={() => copyCodeToClipboard(generateArduinoCode())}\n                className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl text-[10.5px] font-bold bg-[#12141C] hover:bg-[#252936] border border-white/5 hover:border-slate-700 text-slate-300 transition-all active:scale-95 cursor-pointer\"\n              >\n                {copied ? <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" /> : <Clipboard className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-cyan-400\" />}\n                {copied ? \'Copiado!\' : \'Copiar C++\'}\n              </button>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Warning panel about mDNS and CORS */}\n            <div className=\"mb-4 flex items-start gap-2.5 bg-yellow-950/10 border border-yellow-800/30 p-3 rounded-2xl\">\n              <AlertTriangle className=\"w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n              <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-0.5\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-yellow-500 font-mono\">DICA DE ARQUITETURA MULTI-N\303\223 (P2P Wi-Fi)</span>\n                <p className=\"text-[9px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-mono\">\n                  O firmware gerado habilita automaticamente os cabe\303\247alhos de <strong className=\"text-slate-300\">CORS (*)</strong> para o ESPAsyncWebServer. Isso possibilita que os n\303\263s troquem dados diretamente em chamadas AJAX transparentes no navegador dos usu\303\241rios, descobrindo uns aos outros nativamente no Wi-Fi sem a necessidade de um servidor de nuvem externo!\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Code display window */}\n            <div className=\"relative bg-[#12141C] rounded-2xl border border-white/5 max-h-[380px] overflow-auto shadow-inner\">\n              <pre className=\"p-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 leading-normal whitespace-pre selection:bg-cyan-500 selection:text-slate-950\">\n                {generateArduinoCode()}\n              </pre>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-500 mt-3\">\n              <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1\">\n                <Cpu className=\"w-3 h-3 text-cyan-500 animate-pulse\" />\n                Configura\303\247\303\243o Din\303\242mica baseada nos pinos em uso\n              </span>\n              <span>BaudRate sugerido: 115200 bps</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </>\n      ) : (\n        <OtaUpdate nodes={nodes} onAddLog={onAddLog} />\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}bps</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}"
